WEBVTT

1
00:12:22.116 --> 00:12:23.576
Stop it!

2
00:12:42.136 --> 00:12:44.555
Eve!

3
00:12:45.098 --> 00:12:47.100
Why don't you try

4
00:12:47.141 --> 00:12:50.353
the most delicious
fruit in paradise?

5
00:12:55.316 --> 00:12:57.986
It's an apple!

6
00:12:58.111 --> 00:13:00.613
Try it!

7
00:13:03.658 --> 00:13:04.742
No!

8
00:13:04.867 --> 00:13:05.910
Don't touch it.

9
00:13:05.952 --> 00:13:08.037
- Why not?
- It's forbidden.

10
00:13:12.500 --> 00:13:13.626
Here.

11
00:13:13.876 --> 00:13:15.378
This is more beautiful.

12
00:13:15.795 --> 00:13:18.881
Don't listen to him!

13
00:13:19.590 --> 00:13:21.259
But I'm hungry.

14
00:13:23.553 --> 00:13:25.638
You can't eat the fruit of that tree.

15
00:13:28.641 --> 00:13:29.726
Here.

16
00:13:30.435 --> 00:13:31.561
Eat this.

17
00:13:31.978 --> 00:13:36.190
The apple tastes better!

18
00:13:36.607 --> 00:13:39.944
That's why it's forbidden!

19
00:13:40.862 --> 00:13:42.113
Don't listen to him.

20
00:13:43.281 --> 00:13:44.282
Let's go.

21
00:13:44.324 --> 00:13:45.992
Don't go!

22
00:13:46.034 --> 00:13:48.161
The apple is red...

23
00:13:48.453 --> 00:13:49.954
Sweet...

24
00:13:51.247 --> 00:13:53.249
Delicious!

25
00:16:43.669 --> 00:16:46.380
Eve!

26
00:16:47.965 --> 00:16:51.719
Follow me. Eve!

27
00:16:52.678 --> 00:16:56.766
Come and eat the apple!

28
00:17:03.689 --> 00:17:07.485
Adam can't see you!

29
00:17:11.906 --> 00:17:14.450
What are you waiting for?

30
00:17:15.076 --> 00:17:18.371
Try the forbidden fruit!

31
00:17:22.875 --> 00:17:26.087
You'll see. you'll like it!

32
00:17:29.298 --> 00:17:31.259
Do it!

33
00:17:32.301 --> 00:17:33.928
The forbidden fruit?

34
00:17:34.136 --> 00:17:35.471
Forbidden by who?

35
00:17:35.888 --> 00:17:37.223
And how do you know?

36
00:17:37.265 --> 00:17:39.892
And if it's forbidden. why do
you keep telling me to eat it?

37
00:17:40.518 --> 00:17:41.852
Let go of me!

38
00:17:44.146 --> 00:17:45.565
I was only looking!

39
00:17:45.982 --> 00:17:48.734
Can't I even look at
the forbidden fruit?

40
00:17:49.026 --> 00:17:50.027
Answer me!

41
00:17:50.069 --> 00:17:51.904
Are we forbidden
even to look at it?!

42
00:17:51.946 --> 00:17:52.989
Tell me!

43
00:17:53.656 --> 00:17:54.657
No.

44
00:17:54.699 --> 00:17:56.242
Then I'm going to look at it.

45
00:17:57.034 --> 00:17:59.787
If you eat it.

46
00:18:00.746 --> 00:18:03.416
your life will change.

47
00:18:04.125 --> 00:18:05.585
That's enough.
Come on. let's go.

48
00:18:05.585 --> 00:18:06.586
Where?

49
00:18:06.627 --> 00:18:09.463
To take another dip in the pool?
To watch another sunset?

50
00:18:09.630 --> 00:18:10.673
And then?

51
00:18:11.007 --> 00:18:12.633
Then what?
I don't understand you.

52
00:18:12.633 --> 00:18:13.968
I can't explain.

53
00:18:14.010 --> 00:18:16.804
Every day here is the same.
Nothing ever happens.

54
00:18:16.846 --> 00:18:18.306
What do you want to happen?

55
00:18:18.347 --> 00:18:19.682
I don't know.

56
00:18:20.266 --> 00:18:23.060
Something different.
something exciting.

57
00:18:23.269 --> 00:18:24.478
Don't you feel
like you need it?

58
00:18:24.520 --> 00:18:26.063
Why? I'm happy with
the way things are.

59
00:18:26.063 --> 00:18:27.857
Oh. yes? Well. I'm not!

60
00:18:27.898 --> 00:18:29.066
Eve!

61
00:18:33.237 --> 00:18:34.238
Don't eat it!

62
00:18:39.076 --> 00:18:40.786
But it's only an apple.

63
00:18:42.580 --> 00:18:43.706
No. don't eat it.

64
00:18:47.460 --> 00:18:48.836
It's nice.

65
00:18:53.215 --> 00:18:54.925
Try it. It's sweet!

66
00:19:04.769 --> 00:19:06.270
If you eat it.

67
00:19:06.896 --> 00:19:08.439
your life will change.

68
00:20:48.664 --> 00:20:49.915
What's happening?!

69
00:20:51.792 --> 00:20:52.835
I don't know.

70
00:21:00.551 --> 00:21:01.635
Help!

71
00:21:04.764 --> 00:21:06.140
I'm coming!

72
00:21:17.359 --> 00:21:18.402
Help!

73
00:21:19.862 --> 00:21:20.946
Give me your hand!

74
00:21:22.364 --> 00:21:23.449
Come on!

75
00:21:24.700 --> 00:21:25.701
That's it!

76
00:21:26.494 --> 00:21:27.536
That's right!

77
00:21:35.252 --> 00:21:36.337
Come on!

78
00:21:45.971 --> 00:21:47.014
Keep going!

79
00:21:58.192 --> 00:21:59.235
Don't stop!

80
00:22:32.518 --> 00:22:33.727
What is it?

81
00:22:40.401 --> 00:22:41.652
Come on. let's get out of here!

82
00:22:51.161 --> 00:22:52.246
Run!

83
00:22:54.290 --> 00:22:55.332
Jump!

84
00:23:07.928 --> 00:23:08.971
Come on.

85
00:23:12.182 --> 00:23:13.309
Are you okay?

86
00:23:21.650 --> 00:23:23.277
Where do you think
we've ended up?

87
00:23:24.153 --> 00:23:25.654
How will we get out of here?

88
00:23:28.532 --> 00:23:29.867
Answer me!

89
00:23:37.625 --> 00:23:39.168
Follow me!

90
00:23:42.254 --> 00:23:43.464
Wait!

91
00:24:01.523 --> 00:24:02.900
No. don't look at me.

92
00:24:03.150 --> 00:24:04.610
I said don't look at me!

93
00:24:48.445 --> 00:24:49.905
There's nothing left.

94
00:24:51.031 --> 00:24:52.032
Nothing!

95
00:25:09.258 --> 00:25:10.426
I'm tired.

96
00:25:10.759 --> 00:25:12.177
When are we going to stop?

97
00:25:14.680 --> 00:25:15.723
I don't know.

98
00:25:15.764 --> 00:25:17.766
Let's stop. I'm cold.

99
00:25:18.017 --> 00:25:19.518
Why doesn't the sun warm us?

100
00:25:19.560 --> 00:25:20.853
We've lost its warmth.

101
00:25:20.894 --> 00:25:23.147
Thanks to you. we'll
never feel it again.

102
00:25:23.272 --> 00:25:25.399
But without the sun there
won't be any more trees

103
00:25:25.399 --> 00:25:27.401
or food or fruit.

104
00:25:27.609 --> 00:25:29.987
I hope for our sake that you
don't find any more fruit.

105
00:25:32.031 --> 00:25:33.073
Get moving.

106
00:25:33.157 --> 00:25:35.492
We need to find shelter
for the night or we'll die.

107
00:25:36.243 --> 00:25:37.911
Why? Aren't we already dead?

108
00:25:38.037 --> 00:25:40.664
This isn't death.
This is a punishment.

109
00:25:40.706 --> 00:25:41.832
A punishment?

110
00:25:41.874 --> 00:25:44.126
So that means it'll end
and we can go back!

111
00:25:44.251 --> 00:25:47.087
And I swear I'll be
good and obedient.

112
00:25:51.550 --> 00:25:53.927
Don't go!
Wait for me!

113
00:25:56.513 --> 00:25:57.765
Wait for me!

114
00:25:58.098 --> 00:25:59.641
Don't always be so angry!

115
00:25:59.683 --> 00:26:00.893
Wait for me!

116
00:26:53.320 --> 00:26:54.488
What are these?

117
00:27:07.126 --> 00:27:08.168
Hey!

118
00:27:12.506 --> 00:27:14.216
Look what I've found!

119
00:27:24.893 --> 00:27:26.019
Look out!

120
00:28:11.231 --> 00:28:12.399
Come and eat.

121
00:28:13.650 --> 00:28:14.860
We can't!

122
00:28:15.360 --> 00:28:16.653
The animals do.

123
00:29:01.365 --> 00:29:02.449
What is it?

124
00:29:03.408 --> 00:29:04.534
There's somebody there!

125
00:29:04.618 --> 00:29:05.744
Where?

126
00:29:06.119 --> 00:29:07.788
Up there. behind those rocks.

127
00:29:08.413 --> 00:29:10.165
Ah. it's probably just an animal.

128
00:29:10.624 --> 00:29:12.125
It wasn't an animal!

129
00:29:12.209 --> 00:29:13.418
What else could it have been?

130
00:29:13.418 --> 00:29:15.128
- It was a man!
- Aman?

131
00:29:15.170 --> 00:29:16.505
What are you talking about?

132
00:29:17.089 --> 00:29:18.840
I'm telling you it
wasn't an animal!

133
00:29:19.716 --> 00:29:21.426
You're mistaken.
We're the only ones here.

134
00:29:22.636 --> 00:29:23.637
Come on. let's go.

135
00:29:57.963 --> 00:29:59.548
So there wasn't anybody. eh?

136
00:30:10.058 --> 00:30:11.310
Where did they come from?

137
00:30:11.601 --> 00:30:13.186
I told you there was
somebody there.

138
00:30:13.228 --> 00:30:14.521
but you never believe me!

139
00:30:15.981 --> 00:30:17.107
Try to run away.

140
00:30:17.274 --> 00:30:18.817
Where am I supposed to go?

141
00:30:19.151 --> 00:30:20.485
There are so many of them!

142
00:30:21.445 --> 00:30:22.654
Try anyway!

143
00:30:23.280 --> 00:30:24.323
Go!

144
00:30:26.700 --> 00:30:28.035
What are you looking at?

145
00:30:31.913 --> 00:30:33.415
They're getting closer...

146
00:30:33.665 --> 00:30:34.791
What do you want?!

147
00:30:35.917 --> 00:30:36.960
They don't understand us.

148
00:30:37.002 --> 00:30:38.712
Do something!
I don't want them to touch me!

149
00:30:41.423 --> 00:30:43.383
Get off me!
Don't touch me!

150
00:30:50.140 --> 00:30:52.225
- Are you okay?
- Can't you tell?

151
00:30:52.309 --> 00:30:53.977
I told you to run for it.

152
00:30:55.812 --> 00:30:57.647
All you do is criticize me.

153
00:30:57.647 --> 00:30:59.274
You never say anything nice.

154
00:31:00.067 --> 00:31:01.193
I love you!

155
00:31:01.735 --> 00:31:02.778
Finally!

156
00:31:02.778 --> 00:31:04.571
But does this really
seem like the time?

157
00:31:05.364 --> 00:31:07.199
I'm ready to forgive
you for everything.

158
00:31:07.657 --> 00:31:09.201
To die for you.

159
00:31:09.201 --> 00:31:11.161
Or to live together
with you forever!

160
00:31:11.328 --> 00:31:12.371
What?

161
00:31:13.497 --> 00:31:14.581
Together?

162
00:31:14.956 --> 00:31:16.166
Forever?

163
00:31:16.792 --> 00:31:18.335
And who'll give the orders?

164
00:31:19.211 --> 00:31:20.462
Who do you think?

165
00:31:21.004 --> 00:31:22.047
Me. of course!

166
00:31:22.047 --> 00:31:23.090
ow!

167
00:32:28.071 --> 00:32:29.781
Do you think they want to eat us?

168
00:32:34.119 --> 00:32:36.663
Maybe they're not
as nasty as they look.

169
00:32:42.043 --> 00:32:43.503
Stop touching me!

170
00:32:52.304 --> 00:32:54.055
Get your hands off me!

171
00:32:57.142 --> 00:32:58.393
Stop it!

172
00:33:02.772 --> 00:33:04.441
They want to kill me. Help!

173
00:33:04.441 --> 00:33:06.485
They just want to see
how you're made.

174
00:33:13.742 --> 00:33:14.868
No!

175
00:33:48.026 --> 00:33:49.569
They're scared of that creature.

176
00:34:48.712 --> 00:34:50.463
They're scared of us now.

177
00:34:52.299 --> 00:34:53.300
Let's get out of here.

178
00:35:03.685 --> 00:35:04.853
I want to stop.

179
00:35:05.478 --> 00:35:08.106
- We need to get to the sea.
- Why to the sea?!

180
00:35:08.315 --> 00:35:09.941
Because the sea is where life begins.

181
00:35:10.317 --> 00:35:11.776
And we need to start over.

182
00:35:12.110 --> 00:35:13.903
Maybe there isn't a sea here.

183
00:35:14.029 --> 00:35:16.031
Maybe it only
existed up there.

184
00:35:19.451 --> 00:35:20.952
Did you hear what I said?

185
00:35:26.833 --> 00:35:28.335
Hey. are you listening to me?!

186
00:35:28.960 --> 00:35:30.170
No. what did you say?

187
00:35:30.170 --> 00:35:32.255
See? You never listen to me!

188
00:35:32.339 --> 00:35:34.507
I said that there's
no sea around here.

189
00:35:34.549 --> 00:35:35.800
It doesn't exist.

190
00:35:35.967 --> 00:35:37.135
It must exist.

191
00:35:37.552 --> 00:35:38.678
Look.

192
00:35:39.179 --> 00:35:40.764
The birds will lead us to the sea.

193
00:35:40.764 --> 00:35:43.058
Oh. really?
And how do you know?

194
00:35:43.266 --> 00:35:44.684
Because I know.

195
00:35:45.560 --> 00:35:49.022
Sure. like the sun that doesn't warm
the empty land. the--

196
00:35:49.105 --> 00:35:50.940
So where do you want to go?

197
00:35:53.193 --> 00:35:54.778
Somewhere beautiful

198
00:35:54.986 --> 00:35:55.987
and calm.

199
00:35:56.780 --> 00:35:58.990
Not too cold and not too hot.

200
00:35:59.157 --> 00:36:00.575
Where there are trees.

201
00:36:00.784 --> 00:36:03.495
Where there's fruit to eat
and where the animals are friendly.

202
00:36:03.870 --> 00:36:06.331
We were in a place like that.
but thanks to you...

203
00:36:06.456 --> 00:36:08.708
That again?! You said
you'd forgiven me!

204
00:36:08.708 --> 00:36:10.001
Of course I've forgiven you.

205
00:36:10.043 --> 00:36:13.797
But I've never forgiven myself for
letting you persuade me to follow you.

206
00:36:14.130 --> 00:36:15.215
I was wrong.

207
00:36:16.383 --> 00:36:18.843
And now it's you
who must follow me.

208
00:36:18.885 --> 00:36:20.637
Well. I'm not coming with you!

209
00:36:21.137 --> 00:36:22.597
Look. more birds.

210
00:36:22.597 --> 00:36:24.099
all going in the same direction.

211
00:36:24.140 --> 00:36:26.351
They're going towards the forest.
towards the desert!

212
00:36:26.976 --> 00:36:27.977
Maybe.

213
00:36:28.019 --> 00:36:30.271
But after crossing the
forest and the desert.

214
00:36:30.313 --> 00:36:31.648
we'll reach the sea.

215
00:36:32.524 --> 00:36:35.151
But if we go this way the trees
will shade us from the sun.

216
00:36:35.735 --> 00:36:38.154
No. that's the way we need to go.
The sea is that way.

217
00:36:38.321 --> 00:36:39.781
You're always so stubborn!

218
00:36:39.823 --> 00:36:41.950
You go that way.
I'm staying here!

219
00:36:42.450 --> 00:36:44.160
Where are you going?
Come back here!

220
00:36:44.744 --> 00:36:47.497
I want to find out what
I can see from up here.

221
00:36:48.748 --> 00:36:50.458
Where are you?
Come down right now!

222
00:36:50.458 --> 00:36:51.710
No!

223
00:36:51.751 --> 00:36:52.961
You'll hurt yourself.

224
00:36:52.961 --> 00:36:55.463
Go follow your birds.
I'm not coming!

225
00:36:56.047 --> 00:36:57.048
Oh. yes?

226
00:36:57.173 --> 00:36:59.551
If you don't come down
right now. I'm leaving!

227
00:36:59.551 --> 00:37:01.511
Go! I'll be fine without you.

228
00:37:01.678 --> 00:37:02.887
We'll see about that.

229
00:37:04.639 --> 00:37:05.640
I'm going.

230
00:39:40.420 --> 00:39:41.671
Let go of me!

231
00:39:44.966 --> 00:39:46.217
Who are you?!

232
00:39:58.062 --> 00:39:59.856
What do you want from me?
Put me down!

233
00:40:09.991 --> 00:40:11.326
Let go of me!

234
00:40:14.203 --> 00:40:15.496
Don't touch me!

235
00:45:23.221 --> 00:45:24.305
No!

236
00:45:24.347 --> 00:45:26.766
Help me. green man!

237
00:45:28.476 --> 00:45:30.019
My friend!

238
00:45:36.692 --> 00:45:37.860
Let go of me!

239
00:45:39.070 --> 00:45:40.112
No!

240
00:46:24.907 --> 00:46:26.242
Finally. water!

241
00:46:31.497 --> 00:46:34.083
Now I can wash off this
horrible green stuff!

242
00:46:35.209 --> 00:46:36.752
Why don't you wash. too?

243
00:46:38.129 --> 00:46:40.172
The water washes everything away.

244
00:46:40.298 --> 00:46:41.424
Look!

245
00:46:42.967 --> 00:46:44.010
Do what I'm doing.

246
00:46:44.218 --> 00:46:45.761
Come on. do it!

247
00:46:50.391 --> 00:46:52.101
Come on! Hurry up!

248
00:46:53.227 --> 00:46:55.479
You'll see. you'll be much more
handsome afterwards!

249
00:46:56.147 --> 00:46:57.481
Come on!

250
00:47:00.192 --> 00:47:01.319
Jump in.

251
00:47:03.154 --> 00:47:05.448
That's the way!
Good work!

252
00:47:06.991 --> 00:47:08.200
That's it!

253
00:47:09.660 --> 00:47:11.287
See?

254
00:52:56.548 --> 00:52:58.592
No! No!

255
00:53:06.558 --> 00:53:07.851
Let go of me!

256
00:53:08.143 --> 00:53:09.687
Let go of me!

257
00:58:00.477 --> 00:58:01.853
No!

258
00:58:58.744 --> 00:59:00.620
- Don't touch her.
- Oh. no!

259
00:59:02.622 --> 00:59:04.041
I told you not to touch her!

260
00:59:45.832 --> 00:59:47.000
No!

261
01:00:09.064 --> 01:00:10.232
Let go of me.

262
01:01:50.582 --> 01:01:51.833
Are you tired?

263
01:01:57.797 --> 01:01:59.341
You're angry.

264
01:01:59.799 --> 01:02:02.886
But I'm happy.
Very happy.

265
01:02:03.929 --> 01:02:06.431
Because now I know
that you love me.

266
01:02:15.899 --> 01:02:17.776
You came back for me!

267
01:02:18.235 --> 01:02:19.903
You fought for me.

268
01:02:20.862 --> 01:02:22.614
You were wonderful!

269
01:02:24.574 --> 01:02:27.535
And what have you
been doing all this time?

270
01:02:28.078 --> 01:02:30.830
What have I been doing?
Realizing that I loved you.

271
01:02:31.456 --> 01:02:32.916
Ah. really?

272
01:02:33.500 --> 01:02:35.418
Who made you realize it?
That other man?

273
01:02:35.752 --> 01:02:37.337
He didn't mean anything!

274
01:02:39.756 --> 01:02:41.299
Nothing at all.

275
01:03:00.026 --> 01:03:01.444
Is that staff for me?

276
01:03:02.070 --> 01:03:03.154
Maybe.

277
01:03:08.118 --> 01:03:09.494
Do you want to learn to use it?

278
01:03:10.996 --> 01:03:12.706
Did you see how he killed the bear?

279
01:05:24.003 --> 01:05:25.463
I want to be with you.

280
01:05:25.922 --> 01:05:27.215
But with others as well.

281
01:05:27.507 --> 01:05:29.551
- Others?
- I saw them together.

282
01:05:29.759 --> 01:05:31.970
They help each other.
They defend each other!

283
01:05:32.470 --> 01:05:34.139
When I saw you
with that other man.

284
01:05:34.139 --> 01:05:35.265
it made me feel bad.

285
01:05:35.306 --> 01:05:36.307
Bad how?

286
01:05:36.349 --> 01:05:37.892
I don't know.
Bad inside.

287
01:05:37.892 --> 01:05:38.977
Jealous?

288
01:05:39.436 --> 01:05:40.437
Yes.

289
01:05:40.478 --> 01:05:42.105
I wanted you to die.

290
01:05:42.439 --> 01:05:44.649
But then I came to save you.

291
01:05:52.031 --> 01:05:53.158
What's the matter?

292
01:05:54.075 --> 01:05:55.743
Nothing. I'm fine.

293
01:05:58.830 --> 01:05:59.998
Shall we go?

294
01:06:00.540 --> 01:06:01.624
Mm-hmm.

295
01:06:11.259 --> 01:06:12.469
Come on.

296
01:07:03.561 --> 01:07:04.812
What are you doing?

297
01:07:05.146 --> 01:07:07.232
I'm making a staff.

298
01:07:07.357 --> 01:07:08.566
Another one?

299
01:07:08.775 --> 01:07:10.109
Yes. I lost the old one.

300
01:07:10.652 --> 01:07:11.986
This one's even better.

301
01:07:12.237 --> 01:07:13.238
And what are you doing?

302
01:07:13.530 --> 01:07:14.781
I'm making a cub.

303
01:07:14.822 --> 01:07:15.990
A cub?!

304
01:07:16.115 --> 01:07:18.368
Like the animals?
- Yes! Like the animals!

305
01:07:18.535 --> 01:07:20.078
That's impossible.

306
01:07:22.413 --> 01:07:24.040
Why don't you believe me?

307
01:07:24.123 --> 01:07:25.917
Hurry up. woman.
it's getting late!

308
01:07:25.917 --> 01:07:28.086
It's your loss if
you don't believe me!

309
01:07:29.921 --> 01:07:31.256
Goodbye!

310
01:07:31.756 --> 01:07:33.299
Oh no. not again!

311
01:07:33.341 --> 01:07:35.009
Where do you think
you're going?

312
01:07:35.510 --> 01:07:37.971
Hey! Come back here!

313
01:07:39.430 --> 01:07:41.516
I refuse to come with you

314
01:07:41.516 --> 01:07:44.561
unless you stop treating
me like your staff!

315
01:07:44.561 --> 01:07:46.145
What are you talking about?

316
01:07:46.145 --> 01:07:47.564
Come on. come back here!

317
01:07:47.564 --> 01:07:49.315
One time I try to do
something by myself

318
01:07:49.357 --> 01:07:50.525
and you don't believe me!

319
01:07:50.567 --> 01:07:52.151
I don't understand what you want!

320
01:07:52.151 --> 01:07:55.029
If this is the way it's going to be.
there's no point us being together!

321
01:07:55.113 --> 01:07:57.824
Careful where you walk.
you might fall!

322
01:07:57.991 --> 01:08:00.326
I know what I'm doing--

323
01:08:00.743 --> 01:08:02.036
I told you!

324
01:08:03.997 --> 01:08:05.623
It's all your fault.

325
01:08:06.916 --> 01:08:08.626
Why are you so angry?

326
01:08:08.626 --> 01:08:10.712
I'm cold and tired.

327
01:08:11.045 --> 01:08:12.589
And I'm making a cub.

328
01:08:13.256 --> 01:08:14.465
What kind of cub?

329
01:08:14.507 --> 01:08:16.092
A cub who looks like you.

330
01:08:16.301 --> 01:08:17.969
- Like me?
- Or maybe like me.

331
01:08:29.856 --> 01:08:31.065
Really?

332
01:08:31.149 --> 01:08:32.692
A cub like me?

333
01:08:34.444 --> 01:08:35.528
Mm-hmm.

334
01:11:02.008 --> 01:11:03.217
Hey...

335
01:11:04.302 --> 01:11:05.762
Hey. wake up!

336
01:11:10.975 --> 01:11:12.059
Come on. let's go.

337
01:11:13.227 --> 01:11:14.312
Where?

338
01:11:15.354 --> 01:11:16.439
Come with me.

339
01:11:23.112 --> 01:11:24.489
I've found a tunnel.

340
01:11:25.281 --> 01:11:26.491
What tunnel?

341
01:11:27.492 --> 01:11:29.827
It should bring us out on
the other side of the mountain.

342
01:11:30.203 --> 01:11:32.038
Maybe this time we'll find the sea.

343
01:11:54.519 --> 01:11:55.895
Where are we?

344
01:11:58.981 --> 01:12:00.233
What do we do?

345
01:12:00.817 --> 01:12:02.276
I don't know.

346
01:12:12.495 --> 01:12:13.788
Go away!

347
01:12:16.290 --> 01:12:17.500
Go away!

348
01:12:20.294 --> 01:12:21.879
Go on. go away!

349
01:12:23.589 --> 01:12:24.924
You nasty beasts!

350
01:12:37.645 --> 01:12:38.729
Go on!

351
01:12:43.901 --> 01:12:45.278
Get out of here!

352
01:13:45.588 --> 01:13:46.881
It's over.

353
01:13:49.383 --> 01:13:51.093
Take it easy. it's over.

354
01:14:24.460 --> 01:14:26.253
Is this your sea?

355
01:14:45.690 --> 01:14:48.192
I can't go on!

356
01:14:50.194 --> 01:14:52.196
I can't take any more!

357
01:14:54.949 --> 01:14:57.535
You need to get up.
We need to build a shelter.

358
01:14:58.119 --> 01:14:59.161
Come with me.

359
01:15:37.199 --> 01:15:38.617
I didn't find anything.

360
01:15:39.660 --> 01:15:41.495
But I'm hungry.

361
01:15:46.250 --> 01:15:48.294
Don't you understand
that I'm hungry?!

362
01:15:51.464 --> 01:15:53.007
We must have faith.

363
01:15:53.841 --> 01:15:57.303
We can't give up now after
all we've been through.

364
01:15:59.472 --> 01:16:01.849
What faith?
It's over!

365
01:17:39.947 --> 01:17:42.241
Don't give up.
You were right.

366
01:17:42.616 --> 01:17:44.326
We can't stop.

367
01:17:44.660 --> 01:17:46.495
We must go on.

368
01:17:46.829 --> 01:17:48.747
Come on. get up.
- No.

369
01:17:48.747 --> 01:17:50.249
- Let's go.
- No.

370
01:17:50.875 --> 01:17:52.626
We have to stop here.

371
01:17:53.043 --> 01:17:54.253
Why?

372
01:17:58.174 --> 01:17:59.758
I can't explain why.

373
01:18:00.467 --> 01:18:02.595
But I feel that our journey is over.

374
01:18:02.887 --> 01:18:04.138
What about the sea?

375
01:18:04.180 --> 01:18:05.514
The sea is here.

376
01:18:05.764 --> 01:18:07.016
It's beneath us.

377
01:18:07.183 --> 01:18:08.601
We need to wait.

378
01:18:09.018 --> 01:18:10.477
The cold will end.

379
01:18:10.769 --> 01:18:12.438
The ice will melt.

380
01:18:12.897 --> 01:18:14.899
And how will we survive?

381
01:18:15.191 --> 01:18:17.526
I don't know.
but something will happen.

382
01:18:18.861 --> 01:18:20.487
We must have faith.

383
01:24:09.920 --> 01:24:11.255
Does it hurt?

384
01:24:12.422 --> 01:24:13.549
Y-yes...

385
01:24:13.757 --> 01:24:15.342
Unfortunately. you have to suffer.

386
01:24:15.759 --> 01:24:17.219
Why?

387
01:24:17.302 --> 01:24:19.638
- Because you have to.
- But I don't want to!

388
01:24:42.536 --> 01:24:44.246
We need to get to the sea.

389
01:24:44.288 --> 01:24:46.039
Why to the sea?

390
01:24:46.582 --> 01:24:48.375
Because the sea is where life begins.

391
01:24:48.834 --> 01:24:50.711
And we need to start over.
